snippet.title: [URDU] 2025 PMWC at EWC Group Stage Day 1 | PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP
snippet.description:
GROUP STAGE DAY 1 | JULY 25

2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP ka aghaaz ho chuka hai ESPORTS WORLD CUP ke sath, aik dhamakedar Group Stage k pehle din ke sath! Tayyar ho jao ek aur shaandaar summer ke liye jab duniya ki top PUBG MOBILE teams Riyadh mein takraayengi glory ,legacy , aur $3,000,000 ke inaam ke liye. Aao mil kar dekhein ke kaunsi teams HEAT ko BEAT kar paengi!

Yeh global showdown duniya bhar ki behtareen squads ko ikattha karta hai, jo sab 2025 PMWC jo k EWC ki taraf sy horha hai jeetne ka khwab le kar tayyar hain. Pehle ka aaghaz dhamakedaar matches ke saath hoga, jo agle teen dinon ki sakht muqabla baazi ka manzar zahir kryga.

Is safar ka aaghaz Group Stage se hoga, jahan 24 teams ko 3 groups mein taqseem kiya gya hai jo Grand Finals ke liye apni jagah banane ke liye takrayen gi. Is stage se top 8 teams seedha Grand Finals mein pohnchyn gi, jabke baaqi 16 teams high pressure Survival Stage mein aamna saamna karen gi aakhri 8 slots ke liye. Grand Finals mein 16 behtareen teams ek doosre ke khilaaf glory, pride, aur championship ka taaj pehnny k liye pury josh se takraengi.

snippet.title: Piya Ghar Aaya - Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan (Asad's Remix)
snippet.description:
All praise to Ustaad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan.

I'm excited to finally share the full version. Thanks for waiting so patiently (most of you :p)
I'm starting off my new series called EIGHT x EIGHT with this track, As a part of this series I'll put out a new song every Thursday for the next 8 weeks

I grew up in Pakistan, and I now live in Canada. My family is from Faisalabad. Growing up, my grandfather listened to a lot of qawwali around me as a kid and that influence never left my dna. After years of making music, I finally did something with a track from Ustaad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan. I also really enjoyed seeing videos of this track from all over the world, specially from home - thank you for sharing those. 

This remix blew up on TikTok, Instagram etc but more importantly, as you can see in this video, it created a beautiful moment for a group of people and that's what music is all about. Ustaad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan's legacy continues to serve moments like this, I'm grateful to have been a vessel. 

Thanks for showing this so much love, lots more music soon

Asad

Tayyar ho jao ek aur shaandaar summer ke liye jab duniya ki top PUBG MOBILE teams Riyadh mein takraayengi glory ,legacy , aur $3,000,000 ke inaam ke liye. Aao mil kar dekhein ke kaunsi teams HEAT ko BEAT kar paengi!

Yeh global showdown duniya bhar ki behtareen squads ko ikattha karta hai, jo sab 2025 PMWC jo k EWC ki taraf sy horha hai jeetne ka khwab le kar tayyar hain. Pehle ka aaghaz dhamakedaar matches ke saath hoga, jo agle teen dinon ki sakht muqabla baazi ka manzar zahir kryga.

Is safar ka aaghaz Group Stage se hoga, jahan 24 teams ko 3 groups mein taqseem kiya gya hai jo Grand Finals ke liye apni jagah banane ke liye takrayen gi. Is stage se top 8 teams seedha Grand Finals mein pohnchyn gi, jabke baaqi 16 teams high pressure Survival Stage mein aamna saamna karen gi aakhri 8 slots ke liye. Grand Finals mein 16 behtareen teams ek doosre ke khilaaf glory, pride, aur championship ka taaj pehnny k liye pury josh se takraengi.

🔥 Ap 2025 PMWC jo k EWC mai horha hai miss nahe krna chahyngy.

Dekho duniya ki top PUBG MOBILE teams ko Riyadh mein apne waqar ke liye takraate hue!
Har match mein high-stakes action ka lutf uthao, jo har dafa is dorh ko badal kar rakh dega.
Apne pasandeeda region aur teamon ko cheer karo jab woh $3,000,000 aur  ke taj k peche bhaag rahe hongy!
Grand Finals mein hoga zabardast SMASH RULE format to tayyar ho jao excitement ke liye!

🔥 SMASH RULE Grand Finals mein kaise kaam karta hai?

Grand Finals ke doosry din ke baad, Match Point Threshold set kiya jata hai jo ke #1 ranked team ke points mai 10 points jamah kr k banta hai. Jo bhi team is threshold ko cross karti hai, usay phir kisi baad wale match mein jeet hasil karni hoti hai taake woh trophy apne naam kar sake, jis match mein woh threshold cross karti hai, agar usi mein jeeti to bhi woh champion nahi banegi.

Agar Match 18 tak koi team SMASH Rule ke zariye title secure nahi karti, to standard rules ke mutabiq sabse zyada total points wali team ko winner declare kiya jata hai.
